{"tid":122492,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學左4.5個鐘仲未搞得掂三手掉頭、S泊位","createTime":"2017-02-16T05:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T01:31:26.000Z","uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47875c21cfc0eaf6ee8c7b36a2b23955559f1911","tid":122492,"uid":52891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"棍van<br />\n做過~10次掉頭<br />\nClutch 吊得唔好，成日令架車向前標<br />\n<br />\n~16次S泊位<br />\n成日臨倒後前，車側個位攞得太出 (正常應該一尺)<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該死左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38431130d9450a06a59b39ced9c36d1cb2771e11","tid":122492,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"轉自動波 唔好哂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n半個鐘  5次內已經識"},{"pid":"15d9e27ae93f57e99fddd6689c406a346433e8b1","tid":122492,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"應該買份保險受益人填屋企人個名先<br />\n死唔死就你自己決定無人阻到你"},{"pid":"55f8d7af59d6eafd0e39bfd85208cb073f14b47e","tid":122492,"uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉自動波 唔好哂錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n半個鐘  5次內已經識</blockquote><br />\n一上車已經識😂<br />\n學左2堂(個半鐘)已經去考 1take pass"},{"pid":"810948e9463bca91fed45ca623827e0061114323","tid":122492,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"可能你吊得太高，如果左腳控制唔到，試下印住brake吊<br />\nＳ泊位其實係固定公式...唯有練多啲"},{"pid":"2665d89222766205577676f724264fd7c3e826d2","tid":122492,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"覺得高左咪un低小小"},{"pid":"f46ac9a51e890aac42670a84fe621f024215dc95","tid":122492,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"你搵到g點之後左腳hold實 唔好郁 之後全程用break控制速度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"